vetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.inflearn.com/public/files/courses/324145/129d8e36-3974-4ebe-a5fa-e4bd82f8ac0f/speak.gif\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1; height: auto;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; line-height: 2rem; color: rgb(52, 58, 64); font-weight: 500; font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif;\">프로그래밍이 우리에게 자유를 줄 수단이라서가 아닐까요?&nbsp;</h3><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; padding-left: 10px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: inside; list-style-image: initial; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif;\"><li style=\"margin-bottom: 2px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 1.69; color: rgb(73, 80, 87);\">과제를 위한 자료 찾기를 클릭 한 번으로!</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 2px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 1.69; color: rgb(73, 80, 87);\">수많은 거래처에 보낼 문서를 엔터 한 번으로!</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 2px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-all; line-height: 1.69; color: rgb(73, 80, 87);\">매달 해야 하는 반복 업무를 컴퓨터가 자동으로!</li></ul><p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; line-height: 1.69; color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif;\">최근 코딩과 관련된 교육 과목이 증가하면서 프로그래밍과 관련된 교육/직무에 관한 관심도 많이 증가하고 있죠. 게다가 수많은 기업이나 팀에서 코딩을 필수 덕목으로 생각하기 시작했어요.&nbsp;<span style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; background-color: rgb(251, 238, 184);\">대기업 입사 면접에서 비전공자들에게 파이썬 할 줄 아냐고 물어보기도 하죠.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px; padding-top: 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; line-height: 1.69; color: rgb(73, 80, 87); font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif;\">프로그래밍을 취미로 투잡하는 사람들, 여행 다니며 일하는 만들고 싶은 것을 만드는 노마드 인생을 즐기는 사람들도 늘어나고 있어요.</p><div style=\"margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 24px; border: 1px solid rgb(233, 236, 239); vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Apple SD Gothic Neo&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, sans-serif; border-radius: 8px; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250);\"><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 22px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; line-height: 1.45; color: rgb(52, 58, 64); font-weight: 500; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word;\">하지만 코딩은 어쩐지<br style=\"letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word;\">어렵게 느껴지지 않나요?</span></h3><div class=\"card-wrapper card-wrapper-2\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap;\"><div class=\"card-el\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; padding-right: 8px; padding-left: 8px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; width: 325px; flex: 1 0 auto;\"><div style=\"margin-top: 16px; padding: 24px; border: 1px solid rgb(233, 236, 239); vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; border-radius: 8px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 30px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; line-height: 1.69; color: rgb(73, 80, 87); text-align: center;\">🥺</p><p style=\"padding-top: 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; line-height: 1.69; color: rgb(73, 80, 87); text-align: center;\">코딩 강의가 너무 비싼데, 강의 내용이 좋을지 모르겠어요. 한두 번 듣고 안 들을까 봐 걱정돼요.</p></div></div><div class=\"card-el\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; padding-right: 8px; padding-left: 8px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; width: 325px; flex: 1 0 auto;\"><div style=\"margin-top: 16px; padding: 24px; border: 1px solid rgb(233, 236, 239); vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; border-radius: 8px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 30px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; line-height: 1.69; color: rgb(73, 80, 87); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word;\">🥲</span></p><p style=\"padding-top: 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; line-height: 1.69; color: rgb(73, 80, 87); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word;\">혼자 코딩 공부 중인데, 제가 하는 게 맞는지 모르겠어요. 모르는 건 누구한테 질문해야 하나요?</span></p></div></div></div><div class=\"card-wrapper card-wrapper-2\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap;\"><div class=\"card-el\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; padding-right: 8px; padding-left: 8px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; width: 325px; flex: 1 0 auto;\"><div style=\"padding: 24px; border: 1px solid rgb(233, 236, 239); vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; border-radius: 8px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 30px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; line-height: 1.69; color: rgb(73, 80, 87); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word;\">🤔</span></p><p style=\"padding-top: 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; line-height: 1.69; color: rgb(73, 80, 87); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word;\">무작정 시작해도 되는 건가요? 어떤 걸 어떻게 공부해야 할지 모르겠어요.</span></p></div></div><div class=\"card-el\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; padding-right: 8px; padding-left: 8px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; width: 325px; flex: 1 0 auto;\"><div style=\"padding: 24px; border: 1px solid rgb(233, 236, 239); vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; border-radius: 8px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"border: 0px; font-size: 30px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; line-height: 1.69; color: rgb(73, 80, 87); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word;\">🤨</span></p><p style=\"padding-top: 10px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word; line-height: 1.69; color: rgb(73, 80, 87); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word;\">시간도 없고 학원도 너무 멀어서 코딩 공부를 시작하기가 쉽지 않아요.</span></p><div><span style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.3px; word-break: break-word;\"><br></span></div></div></div></div></div>', '이미 2만명 이상이 학습하고 만족한 최고의 프로그래밍 입문 강의. 인프런이 비전공자 위치에서 직접 기획하고 준비한 프로그래밍 입문 강의로, 프로그래밍을 전혀 접해보지 못한 사람부터 실제 활용 가능한 프로그래밍 능력까지 갈 수 있도록 도와주는 강의입니다.', '1', 'Python', 'Array', '2024-11-27 05:35:30', 0, 40);
